{"tid":1823897,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"史上首例！美科學家用青蛙幹細胞 打造「活體」機器人","createTime":"2020-01-14T04:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T06:22:09.000Z","uid":32511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c2dcf70c03f9a77f9e45cdafd506ddc21dc2e7e3","tid":1823897,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:54:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XLI7VtjgOyk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXLI7VtjgOyk&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=a42e1463\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XLI7VtjgOyk</a><br />\n<br />\n美國研究人員利用非洲爪蛙的幹細胞，創造出史上首個「活體」微型機器人，最成功的案例是有兩條短腿，能靠自己的力量活動。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員希望透過程式編寫，讓這些活體機器人能在人類體內輸送藥物、穿過人體動脈清除斑塊，或是在海中去除有毒的塑膠微粒。由於它們是活體機器人，因此若是損壞或撕裂，能自行複製和修復。<br />\n<br />\n佛蒙特大學電腦科學和機器人專家邦加德（Joshua Bongard）說，「這些都是新的活體機器人。它們既不是傳統的機器人，也不是一般動物。它們是一種活體、可程式編寫的生物體」。<br />\n<br />\n波士頓塔芙茨大學（Tufts University）艾倫探索中心（Allen Discovery Center）主任萊文（Michael Levin）說，「這些都是全新的生命形態。它們從未在地球上存在過」。<br />\n<br />\n機器人專家傾向用金屬和塑膠來提高強度和耐用度，但萊文和同事發現用生物組織製造機器人的好處。受損的活體機器人能自癒傷口，一旦完成任務後就會自我瓦解，就像自然生物死亡時會腐爛一樣。<br />\n<br />\n這些機器人的長度不到一毫米，是透過超級電腦運行的「演化式演算法」所設計。萊文表示，它們體積很小，但最終計畫是將它們按比例縮放。<br />\n<br />\n但佛蒙特大學研究團隊博士生克瑞曼（Sam Kriegman）坦言，這項工作引發道德問題，特別是考慮到未來的活體機器人可能具有神經系統，並具有認知能力，進而變得更加活躍，但不太擔心會對人類構成威脅。"},{"pid":"e9aa296351498db9d24def1e4a1e87276e9d95f3","tid":1823897,"uid":168394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:56:38.000Z","msg":"skynet"},{"pid":"5ecaa4e520c4eb67acf7c2b2aa7c5c7cc597fd78","tid":1823897,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3228ae8bc577ad51904d7a523e55dd9ac1d365","tid":1823897,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:03:51.000Z","msg":"異形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617ad17175301c8d4bb46439d03331f7c5a9fe76","tid":1823897,"uid":86,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"智能叛變"},{"pid":"8fe0000d4da6c5caff2d5f7bebfaaa045657fd0b","tid":1823897,"uid":269269,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"咁算唔算生命？<br />\n換言之完成任務就殺咗佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f42d8f66e73cfa18a23a22c86d627e6b76506bb","tid":1823897,"uid":53672,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:08:44.000Z","msg":"篇文美國變中國 實比連登仔屌死"},{"pid":"42ef1a64a74de437464d0888e2ba039803cab23f","tid":1823897,"uid":221395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:08:58.000Z","msg":"［行動Po］一月十九 天下制裁大遊行 大家幫手推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822183\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822183</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eb3955c3fce65bdcefcf3d2538d52a6765ce3c1b","tid":1823897,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:03:12.000Z","msg":"留名等睇大哥哥.jpg"},{"pid":"0309fdfff5c1320244782880859f3f0f813145dc","tid":1823897,"uid":224921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"就黎有t800，不得了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}